abstract_ssm: Documents, correspondence, reports, and bird-watching logs compiled by members of the Emirates Bird Records Committee (EBRC), from the 1980s to the early 2000s.  The EBRC, a group of predominantly expatriate volunteers living in the United Arab Emirates, sought to document and verify sightings of various bird species throughout the Emirates.
